PopularMovies Project: An android app that allows users to browse currently popular movies

Before you to build and run this repo, you need to add an API key from themoviesdb.org to the properties.grade file. Follow these step to realise this task:

1) Create an account a themoviesdb.org and request an API key.

2) Go to the gradle.properties file and add your API key

3) Run the app in android studio!
